&lt;p&gt;Vegan Khristolub - a Christian and a pacifist, sentenced in Russia to three years in a penal colony for anti-war statements. The reason was YouTube videos where he criticizes the cult of Stalin and the actions of the Red Army.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SOTAvision editorial office visited him in the Voronezh region: Khristolub lives in seclusion, takes care of the garden and continues to wait for the appeal decision.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He speaks about faith, the church and the war - directly, without slogans. Why do his words frighten the authorities, how he prays for his enemies and for what he is ready to go to prison.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;📺 The full interview film is on YouTube.&lt;/p&gt;

