&lt;b&gt;Now also with parasites and information-propaganda groups. Belarusian Orthodox Church priests are being involved in new spheres of influence on society&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The practice of involving Belarusian Orthodox Church clergy in government events aimed at influencing various groups in society is expanding in Belarus.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This includes purely ideological events, such as the &quot;Single Day of Informing&quot;. Monthly meetings within the framework of &quot;information days&quot; on a given topic are held in labor collectives by information and propaganda groups (IPG).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At least one of these groups - in Zhlobin - included a priest of the Belarusian Orthodox Church, noted &quot;Christian Vision&quot;. Cleric of the parish of the Holy Life-Giving Trinity Church &lt;b&gt;Priest Pavel Kulish&lt;/b&gt; participated in the &quot;Single Day of Informing&quot; on the topic &quot;Belarus - a country of opportunities. Youth policy at the present stage&quot;, which took place on June 24 in the Zhlobin district division of the Ministry of Emergency Situations, &lt;a href=&quot;https://eparhiya.by/2025/06/26/edinyj-den-informirovaniya-v-zhlobinskom-blagochinii/&quot;&gt;reported&lt;/a&gt; the Gomel Diocese.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The meeting promoted the theses that &quot;&lt;i&gt;Belarus is a country of opportunities, in which there are many prospects for development&lt;/i&gt;&quot;, &quot;&lt;i&gt;a state that keeps up with the times and is becoming more and more prosperous every day&lt;/i&gt;&quot;, &quot;&lt;i&gt;a country that gives every citizen the opportunity to realize themselves in any field&lt;/i&gt;&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Directly, Priest Pavel Kulish touched upon the spiritual and moral foundations of a stable society, emphasizing that the family and faith are a solid foundation for the upbringing of the individual, true patriotism and a responsible attitude to one&#x27;s work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And a little earlier in the Mostovskoy District Internal Affairs Department, an event was held with &quot;&lt;i&gt;able-bodied citizens not employed in the economy&lt;/i&gt;&quot;. As &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/DLPSK2uo5G7/?img_index=1&quot;&gt;stated&lt;/a&gt; in the information of the local Department of Labor, Employment and Social Protection, during the &quot;group educational event in the district police department&quot; the unemployed present were &quot;tried to reach&quot; by the First Deputy Head of the Mostovskoy District Internal Affairs Department, Deputy Head of the Department of Labor, Employment and Social Protection, psychologist of the CSON, Rector of the Church of the Icon of the Mother of God &quot;Joy of All Who Sorrow&quot; &lt;b&gt;Vladimir Saverchenko&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Such meetings with &quot;parasites&quot; are held as part of a republican campaign: district police departments, together with labor and employment departments, district commissions to promote employment, &quot;work out&quot; citizens who are in the database of those not employed in the economy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From &lt;b&gt;April 1, 2025&lt;/b&gt;, the Ministry of Internal Affairs is implementing the &quot;Complex of Additional Measures to Provide Preventive Impact on Able-Bodied Citizens Not Employed in the Economy&quot;. Officially unemployed people who have been included in the lists of &quot;not employed in the economy&quot; are massively summoned to the district police departments, and from there they are sent to the Employment Centers for employment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The presence of a priest at such an event in the police &quot;Christian Vision&quot; noticed for the first time.&lt;/p&gt;

