&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rocket attack on Prykarpattia: a woman was injured, a Ukrainian Greek Catholic Church (UGCC) temple was damaged&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the early morning of June 29, Russian troops carried out a missile strike on the Ivano-Frankivsk region. As a result of the debris falling, one woman in the village of Naraivka was injured and hospitalized. A residential house was also damaged.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the village of Vasyuchin of the Rohatyn community, the debris &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/SvitlIana.Onyshchuk/posts/pfbid02graiKqXp4M9W5yXenHUfN5N9yc6dWYcktkSKfzXm4cb4ahcwNJV1XEiWSbkzSXSVl&quot;&gt;damaged&lt;/a&gt; the windows of the building of the Pokrova of the Most Holy Theotokos UGCC temple and partially the wooden bell tower.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The photo shows the temple before the damage.&lt;/p&gt;

#ukraine #ugcc #destruction

