&lt;b&gt;Russian nun reported new gratitudes from military units&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The head of the &quot;Help the Brothers&quot; group, nun &lt;b&gt;Evgenia (Tsivtsivadze)&lt;/b&gt;, shared another round of awards from the Russian military.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This time it was a &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.me/PomoshBratiyam/17051&quot;&gt;letter of gratitude&lt;/a&gt; from the command of military unit 51831 and the medal &quot;For Assistance to the Front&quot;, as well as a &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.me/PomoshBratiyam/17049&quot;&gt;certificate&lt;/a&gt; from the volunteer detachment &quot;Nevsky&quot; of the Russian Ministry of Defense.&lt;/p&gt;

