&lt;b&gt;The Russian Ministry of Justice recognized the lawyer of conscientious objectors as a &quot;foreign agent&quot;&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On Friday, the Russian Ministry of Justice included &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.me/localissues/&quot;&gt;Artem Klygue&lt;/a&gt; - a lawyer for the &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.me/stoparmy&quot;&gt;Conscientious Objectors Movement&lt;/a&gt;, who defends the right of Russian citizens to refuse to participate in the war on grounds of conscience - in the register of &quot;foreign agents&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He has already stated that he will appeal the decision of the Ministry of Justice.&lt;/p&gt;

#russia #objectors

