&lt;p&gt;Cardinal &lt;b&gt;Kurt Koch,&lt;/b&gt; Prefect of the Dicastery for Promoting Christian Unity, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vaticannews.va/be/kaciol/news/2025-07/kardynal-koch-malitva-za-ukrainu.html&quot;&gt;spoke&lt;/a&gt; at the first session of the Synod of the Ukrainian Greek Catholic Church, which began in Rome. He expressed deep solidarity with Ukraine and noted the important role of Ukrainian Greek Catholics in the ecumenical dialogue.&lt;/p&gt;

