&lt;p&gt;The war correspondent of the &quot;International Brigade Pyatnashka&quot;, &lt;b&gt;Elena Sokolova&lt;/b&gt;, told the audience that &quot;&lt;i&gt;the participants of the &#x27;SVO&#x27; are closer to God than any priest, they are ready to give their lives for us, although they don&#x27;t even know us&lt;/i&gt;&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

