&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stripped of Ukrainian citizenship, the Primate of the UOC, Metropolitan Onufriy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Security Service of Ukraine &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/SecurSerUkraine/posts/pfbid02gBAAscdaGuCJSfFuGTetvCtUUKL4iEZSQ1ZvibYeCMiXZ3w2be2DPRCKcA4anR57l&quot;&gt;reports&lt;/a&gt; that President Zelenskyy has stripped &lt;b&gt;Metropolitan Onufriy&lt;/b&gt; (Orest Berezovsky) of Ukrainian citizenship.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The message states:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;According to the information available to the SBU, Berezovsky (Onufriy) maintains contact with the Moscow Patriarchate and deliberately obstructed the canonical independence of the Ukrainian Church from the Moscow Patriarchate, whose representatives openly support the Russian aggression against Ukraine. Despite the full-scale invasion, Berezovsky (Onufriy) continues to effectively support the policy of the Russian Orthodox Church and its leadership, in particular Patriarch Kirill (Gundyaev).&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;

