&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Zelenskyy stripped the citizenship of the primate of the UOC - SBU&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SBU &lt;a href=&quot;https://ssu.gov.ua/novyny/za-materialamy-sbu-prypyneno-hromadianstvo-ukrainy-oresta-berezovskoho-tak-zvanoho-mytropolyta-upts-mp-onufriia&quot;&gt;reported&lt;/a&gt; the termination of Ukrainian citizenship of &lt;b&gt;Orest Berezovsky&lt;/b&gt;, better known as Metropolitan Onufriy of the UOC. The corresponding decree was signed by President &lt;b&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the SBU, Onufriy voluntarily obtained Russian citizenship as early as 2002, but did not inform the Ukrainian authorities about this. Nevertheless, he continued to enjoy the rights of a Ukrainian citizen. Also, according to the intelligence service, he maintained ties with the Moscow Patriarchate and deliberately opposed the granting of autocephaly to the Ukrainian church, despite the full-scale war.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SBU reminds that the head of the Russian Orthodox Church, Patriarch &lt;b&gt;Kirill (Gundyaev)&lt;/b&gt;, blessed the Russian invasion and justifies the genocide of Ukrainians.&lt;/p&gt;

