&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Catholic believer and journalist Tina Palynska, along with the daughter of a human rights defender, have been recognized as political prisoners.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tina and her elder daughter Margarita Rabinovich were detained in May 2025 and placed in custody on a criminal case. The women are being held in a multi-colored house in Vitebsk.&lt;/p&gt;

